 class="t mab1 x73 h28 ya14 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ment that these two things given to Abraham are </div><div class="t mab2 x48 h28 ya15 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the things which give us strong consolation. </div><div class="t mab3 x2c h38 ya16 ff1 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON XXI. </div><div class="t mab4 x42 h2f ya17 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FEBRUARY 22, 2890. </div><div class="t mab5 x40 h2f ya18 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">HEBREWS 9:15-2o. </div><div class="t mab6 x34 he ya19 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. WHAT </div><div class="t m1ba xb h28 y938 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was effected by the blood of the old </div><div class="t m765 x48 h28 ya1a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">covenant? </div><div class="t m136 xc h28 ya1b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m89b x53 h28 ya1c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Was any sin ever removed by that cove-</div><div class="t mab7 x48 h28 ya1d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nant ? </div><div class="t m139 xc h28 ya1e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m370 x53 h28 ya1e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What can the blood of Christ accomplish ? </div><div class="t m13e x5f h28 ya1f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m978 x53 h28 ya20 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What provision is made for transgressors </div><div class="t m12c x48 h28 ya21 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">under the first covenant? Heb. 9:15. </div><div class="t m142 xc h28 ya22 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m833 x53 h28 ya23 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What law did they transgress under the first </div><div class="t m45d x48 h28 ya24 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">covenant. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
